on april 17 1989 the eighth civic department panel composed of 
provincial court judge danuta widawska provincial court judge anna 
borowska provincial court judge jadwiga siwek and protocol clerk 
irmina fila after the recognition on april 17 1989 in warsaw of a 
motion of the registering committee of the independent 
selfgoverned trade union solidarity to enter it into the register 
of trade unions decides 
to enter into the register of trade unions in part b the 
independent selfgoverned trade union solidarity with its 
headquarters in gdansk uniting workers employed on the basis of 
contract at state enterprises or contract with cooperatives 
employed on the basis of membership or nomination at rural 
cooperatives as well as students of factories vocational schools 
working for the factories or being taught a profession those in 
cottage industries people working on basis of an agency contract 
old age pensioners and invalids functioning on the territory of 
the polish peoples republic on the basis of the unions statute 
together with the annex adopted on april 8 1989 and being its 
integral part 
