here are the major features of the 
package president bush unveiled monday to reward poland for its 
recent steps toward democracy and to encourage further political 
and economic reforms 
trade concessions 
the administration will submit to congress legislation to lower 
us tariffs on a variety of polish goods this would be 
accomplished by putting poland under the generalized system of 
