summer cottage to a returning member of the seven ay jackson 
murray was born to the land but he never saw it as the rich 
strong north until jackson showed him how 
he opened my eyes murray says 
to stan black the algoma central railway is more than art and 
recreation it is commerce black a vice president of the company 
says the railroad last year moved 14 million tons of iron ore 
limestone and coke 
the railroad carried an additional 1 million tons of 
manufactured products such as steel and almost half as much timber 
and wood pulp he says 
but there is a shadow across blacks figures eighty percent of 
